<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Rebel Wilson commands attention on screen. </p>

<p>But the 40-year-old actress also knows how to turn heads in traffic, as demonstrated by her car karaoke skills on Monday.</p>

<p>Rebel honed her vocal skills while stuck on a busy Los Angeles commute, and shared footage of her singalong to Instagram. </p>

<p>Pitch perfect! Rebel Wilson certainly knows how to turn heads in traffic, as demonstrated by her car karaoke skills on Monday</p>

<p>Rebel looked relaxed as she sat and danced in the front seat of her 4WD, belting out the Bruno Mars song 24K Magic. </p>

<p>She dressed casually in a blue Nike sweatshirt, which she paired with oversized cat-eye sunglasses. </p>

<p>The comedian wore her blonde hair in a ponytail pushed to one side. </p>

<p>Singing her heart out: Rebel looked relaxed as she sat and danced in the front seat of her 4WD, belting out the Bruno Mars song 24K Magic</p>

<p>It comes as Rebel continues her incredible body transformation. </p>

<p>The star has declared 2020 her 'year of health', and has lost at least 18kg (40lbs or 2.8 stone) so far. </p>

<p>Earlier this month, she drew attention to her shrinking frame while posing for a photo shared with her 8.6 million Instagram followers. </p>

<p>Diet: It comes as Rebel continues her incredible body transformation</p>

<p>She revealed a glimpse of cleavage and her slimmed-down waist in a white top and black pants, as she posed at her home in Los Angeles. </p>

<p>Rebel added a chic red cardigan and white loafers to the look, and swept her blonde locks into a sleek high ponytail.</p>

<p>She was wearing minimal makeup, allowing her natural beauty to shine through. </p>

<p>Blue beauty! Last month, Rebel showed off her slimmed-down physique in a tight blue wrap dress on Instagram (left). Pictured on the right in May 2019  </p>

<p>Slimming down: Earlier this month, she drew attention to her shrinking frame while posing for this photo shared with her 8.6 million Instagram followers</p>

<p>'I made a new friend today x thanks Aunty Hilary,' Rebel captioned the photo, which showed a friend's dog resting its paw on her leg.</p>

<p>Rebel recently returned to Los Angeles, after spending several weeks in her home city of Sydney, Australia. </p>

